# appExtensionIdentity

**Instance Property**

The identifying information for the app extension you want to launch.

## Declaration

```swift
var appExtensionIdentity: AppExtensionIdentity
```

## Discussion

Specify this value at initialization time. Fetch identity information from the [doc://com.apple.extensionfoundation/documentation/ExtensionFoundation/AppExtensionPoint/Monitor] type.
